node.text:
.
.

God didn't f* up when he gave you your desires.

Your desire were placed on your heart on purpose, for you to walk out on this planet.

In today's video I riff on the various desires of my life, from men to money, and how I worked with the divine to bring these things into my life.

Some of what I share:

** Examples of what specific, intentional inspired action has looked like for me

** Why I do not visualize when manifesting

** Letting yourself really want what you really f*ing want

** How to support and back yourself to making sh*t happen

*** I also tell a really beautiful, personal story of how I quite literally *opened the door* to romantic love coming into my life, and being passionately pursued by a wonderful man who is now my partner.

We got some money manifestation vibes and some love manifestation vibes in this video!

Important: We were not able to include the entire video on IGTV today. For the other half -- and the riff on manifesting love -- please visit my youtube.

Call in love: https://youtu.be/TP-XDuSefIU

So, remember: God didn't f* up when he gave you your desires.

You're allowed to want what you want.

And you're meant to go after what you want.

Let me know in the comments below the video: What is something you are shrinking your desires around? What would it be like to own and validate your desires? What would it be like to let yourself want what you want from a confident, empowered, expectant place?

I can't wait to hear from you!

Remember: Your desires are guiding you. You are so worthy. You were made to have it all. I love you.

To watch the second half of this video -- including the story of how I *opened the door* to love -- go to my youtube now.

Open the door to love: https://youtu.be/TP-XDuSefIU

I love you.

node.title: God GAVE you your desire. Heaven and earth will MOVE for you to have them

node.text:
.
Hello hello!

So as you may know, nearly two years ago I bought a house at the edge of West Hollywood and Beverly Hills.

While it was my third property to purchase, it was the first home I bought to live in myself.

When I bought it, I knew it would be the last place I would live as a single woman. I called it "my last single girl house" -- and I did it up EXACTLY as I wanted.

The renovation was a little intense. I gutted a bath room and the kitchen; redid the laundry room; automated everything (it's a full smart house) added plants, trees and beautiful landscaping; and fully furnished the house.

It was a big endeavor, but it's finally complete.

AND it's a whole vibe.

A funny thing happened though, my boyfriend and I got together -- exactly one year ago today actually (happy anniversary, baby) -- and the single girl house is... no longer needed.

I've been using it as a space for work (the office is such a boss woman moment) and I'm almost ready to put it on the market.

(I'm not rushed, but I'm sensing it's almost time.)

The other night, I hosted friends at my house. Before I gave them a tour, my friend @stephanie.gressley asked to record me. This little video is the result.

I thought it was a perfect way to show you guys some of the details and backstory of the now completed house.

My favorite things: Three dishwasher drawers, a beverage station, hot water dispenser, vibes sign, intelligently designed laundry room ;), and the white marble bathroom.

Come on this house tour with me! So much effort, patience, and love went into this house.

You have to see it for yourself!

What's your favorite part? Tell me below!

Special thanks to the @thedadforlife for helping me execute the dream kitchen and for figuring out how to make all my ideas happen; @briannabitton/@bittoninteriors for your guidance in so much of the decor and design; @lifedesignrenovation for the renderings and all your help in the process; @kimhamiltonn_ for having my back always and for calling every kitchen showroom, warehouse and factory in the country; and @girldesigndreams for making this video a video. I appreciate you all so much.

#luxuryhomes #westhollywood #renovations #hometour

node.title: IT'S FINISHED! Come with me on a HOME TOUR!

node.text:
DHL had failed to deliver it the days before because I missed the notification when they were at my gate.

So, I literally made them a code to my gate and authorized the bag to be delivered with no signature.

When I got home from park with kids and realized bag was in fact at my door, I legitimately hugged the box and did a dance through the living room before setting phone on table to document the moment.

It might seem trivial… but the bottom line for me is: We are made to have the life we want.

The passion. The purpose. The love. The work. The fulfillment. And… in my case… The mother fucking Birkin.

#birkin #hermes #idie #iwassonervous #finally

node.text:
.
.
Here is the thing: I live my life as an exception to many rules.

I should not have been a multimillionaire. This life shouldn't be possible, but I created the impossible and that's what I want for people.

In today's video I share on achieving the impossible in our lives. Specifically, riff on....

- Forming a powerful dynamic between you and money.

- Who you are/how you be creates your reality (over what you say).

- The insane power of liking yourself + knowing your worth.

- Getting the power of money into worthy hands (ie: yours).

- Showing up with humanity and love, always. (Lord help us... always.)

- Believing that you are the exception to the rule.

Quotable moments:

* If it sounds too good to be true, then it's what you mother f*Ing deserve.

* Who better than you to have a good life?

* I created the impossible and that's what I want for people. That's why I do this work.

* Money is just opportunity. Money is just options. Money is just energy. Money is just power. Let's get the money in your hands so you can be the empowered one and so you can do the important things.

* It might not look like it's like, it's possible for you, but it can be. And when you know this and you do the impossible, you inspire a lot of people. They now know they can do the impossible too.

* So, they believe the lie that they can't. The lie from their family, society, or their community that says they can't. But I'm going to tell them they can. And when take a chance on themselves and they're going to start to expect new outcomes, a new reality. And they're going to start to walk down a new path and things will unfold differently. I can handle a little online nonsense in the name of that.

* Putting myself in front of a large audience is not always easy. People sometimes say thing about me, but it's worth it to me. It matters to people who have a breakthrough, insight, shift, or ah-ha reading my book or enrolling in one of my courses. It matters to them. And they matter to me.

Get today's audio on the And She Rises podcast. (Episode #119)

I can't wait to hear what you think.

You are worthy. You are deserving. You are good enough.

Do your thing. Live your life.

node.title: You are the exception to the rule

HOWEVER, THERE ARE NO IMPLANTS ON MY BODY.

I HAD A FAT TRANSFER IN 2019. MY BOOBS WERE VERY UNEVEN SO I TOOK SOME FAT OUT OF MY BELLY AND PUT IT IN MY BOOBS AND THIS WAS TOTALLY THE BEST DECISION FOR ME.

AS FAR AS MY FEELINGS ON COSMETIC ENHANCEMENTS...

WE ARE ESSENTIALLY POLICING EACH OTHERS BODIES WHEN WE SAY THAT PEOPLE CAN’T DO XYZ AND IF THEY DO THEY HAVE TO SHARE ABOUT IT IN CERTAIN TIME AND CERTAIN WAY.

WE ARE ALL GROWN ASS WOMEN HERE; WE CAN DO WHAT WE CHOOSE.

MEN AND SOCIETY HAVE POLICED US FOR LONG ENOUGH.

LEAVE EACH OTHER’S BODIES ALONE.

DO WHAT YOU FEEL. DO IT SAFELY. CREATE THE LIFE, LOVE, AND BODY YOU WANT.

I LOVE YOU!

node.text:
So, one time... I finished, edited, and self published a book... during a pandemic.

There were gravely important world events occurring. There was some for real reckoning and healing happening in my own life.

(Life doesn’t pause when you go after a dream. You have to prioritize... and pivot. Over and over.)

I wrote chapter one in NYC during a painful breakup. I wrote chapter eleven in LA as protestors marched down my street and helicopters flew over my house. I finished edits while recovering from the virus with a family member in ICU.

There were also about five million hiccups (as is with doing anything for the first time)... like publishing, distributing, editing and launching issues.

But... we did it! The little book that could had made its way around the world. It was named a best seller on day one.

The first 20,000 copies have now sold. (We are just getting started.)

And... it’s message can be felt.

THE MESSAGE: You are worthy of money. You are capable and deserving. Life is responding to you. Money loves to support you.

Life did not set most of us up for the life we wanted... and yet... it’s still available to us. We can still do, have, be and achieve.

We can still go after it. We can still create a new — and very different — future. It is not too late for us!

You can thrive inside a very supportive relationship with money. You are meant to...

And I can show you how!

My book is called: Rich as F*ck — More Money than You Know What to do With

And it’s available on Amazon, Barnes & Nobel, etc!

We got 800+ five star reviews on Amazon saying this is the book for you! 

Enjoy! Let me know how it serves and supports you!

Q: Should we do one (or more) more book parties? What cities?

Q two: Should I sit my ass down and record an audio book?

Let me know!

(Also... Tag any friends you see in this video!!)

#moneyqueen #richafbook

node.text:
If you haven't been around here long, you may not know that I have a very religious background. I grew up in the middle of the Bible Belt.

As a child, I was very curious about God.

I had myself in church twice a week from the time I was in 5th grade on. My parents dropped me off until the time I could drive. Once I could drive, I was shuttling the other teenagers to church with me.

I have two bible school degrees -- from a ministry training college and from Oral Roberts University.

I say all this to say: I know religious dogma.

I know doctrine. I know all the legalism. I know the rules. I could recite for you every single thing a good Christian girl should and should not do and back them up with (taken out of context) bible verses.

And I know something more powerful than all of that: God.

God's heart. My heart.

I know energy. I understand how the energy by which you do a thing affects the outcome of a thing. I understand intention. I know frequency.

I know that there are people out there right now, giving ten percent to a church who do not understand the energy of abundance, do not know their worth, don't believe in the particular place they are giving their money... And the tithing thing probably isn't working that well for them.

I know other people who truly believe that the reason they are so financially blessed is because of their giving.

They might not know that their belief in the thing is more powerful than the thing, but they are happy with the dynamic at play. And it's working for them.

And, I know from a lot of experience, a lot of years of tithing, and many years now of donating, giving and supporting things I believe in...

That there is a powerful dynamic available -- where generosity and giving are very supportive to you and your desires -- and where guilt, obligation and overcompensating are no longer in the mix...

When you understand the energy at play plus the power of the intention and belief by which you give + receive + donate + tithe... it can be a very powerful, rewarding and incredible thing.

In this vlog, I break it down! Let me know what you think below. Unless it's negative and annoying, then keep it to yourself. Xo.

node.title: God Doesn’t Care if You Tithe! (I said it.)

.
Feel the energy and intention and power of these words as you listen:

I am worthy.

I am good enough.

Money loves me.

I am meant to be supported.

I am meant to be taken and care of.

I am allowed to have a good life.

I welcome now an experience where things become easier for me.

Money is consistent, supportive, and reliable in my life.

My debt is eliminated

My bank accounts are overflowing with money I felt great about receiving

I allow money in.

I invite easier, natural, more fluid, intentional and purposeful relationship with money.

The life of the wealthy woman is available to me.

It's who I am how, it's how I be, and it's what I choose to receive.

It's meant for me. I step into it more and more.

I am okay. I am on my way. I am destined for full and complete greatness.

Ready to move into the experience of feeling supported by money? Ready to heal past money wounds? Ready to forgive past money mistakes? Ready to step further into all your are meant to be when it comes to earning, attracting, generating, receiving, investing, saving, and having more money ? Ready to redefine, rearrange, and recommit to how money works in your life?

Ready to feel fucking good when it comes to your financial life?

Money Mentality Makeover is open for enrollment.

MMM is special. It's sacred. It's unique. It was built over six year to create a full, complete, robust program designed to support you in creating the experiences with money that you desire. You can have a loving, healthy, and supportive relationship with money.

And the time is now.

Success stories + payment options + all the details: http://amandafrances.com/money

There are over 100 testimonials available on the enrollment page help you decide if this course is right for you. Check them out.

See you inside! I can’t wait to see what you do with this content. I love you.

.
Hi loves!

I am thrilled beyond to share this motivating, empowering, and vibey as hell video with you today.

Dance to it. Walk to it. Run to it. Start your day with it. Listen to it any time you need a boost.

Say it with me:

I am worthy. I am here on purpose. I am ready for more. I am ready for my next steps. I take the inspired guidance. It is time for the desires of my heart to take form in my physical reality.

I was made for money. There is nothing wrong with desiring more money. I allow myself to earn, receive, generate, have and keep more and more and more money. I use it will. I spend it well. I save it well. I invest it well. I use it for good. I use it to create the world I want to see, for myself, and for those around me. I trust me.

I know my purpose. I sense and see my path. I make my moves I take my steps My heart is open. I am being guided always.

I loved. I am incredible. I am a child of God and a creation of the most high. I give of my gifts, callings, talents freely and I receive compensations beyond I expected or imaged freely as well.

I step into my next level of abundance. And so it is. Amen.

Music: WOMAN by @bri_thelady

node.text:
.
.
(10,812 to be exact)

Numbers for the sake of numbers is meaningless. Numbers for the sake of measuring goals, impact, influence, wealth, and growth... is kind of a vibe.

It has been an honor and joy to get this book out into the world, to you.

I still get overwhelmed when I see it in your homes, bags and cars. On your coffee tables, on your kindles, in your kitchens, and in your hands as you take a bath.

“Holy shit I wrote a book!” still regularly floats through my mind and comes out my mouth.

Writing and self-publishing has been a journey. And like I said in the video, I don’t regret it. And I’m NOT in a hurry to do it again. lol

Thank you for your love and support. Thank you for having my back. Thank you for being gracious, genuine, and loving humans who make up a very beautiful corner of the internet.

The interwebs can be a wild place, but the vibes are right over here.

I love you. I appreciate you. I’m so excited to watch this book have a life if it’s own.

My prayer: May it be so much bigger than me, my company, or this life. May it grow in momentum, impact, reputation, power, love and transformational energy.

May it support you in being wildly, unabashedly, relentlessly, powerfully and intentionally Rich as Fuck. May it support you in creating freedom, fulfilling desire, and living in abundance.

May we all have more money than we know what to do with. And may we use that money so, so well — creating the world we desire, deserve and want to see.

May we reach deeper, love bigger, go further, and unleash our big loving beautiful hearts, gifts and work on to the world like nothing that’s ever been seen.

And every beautiful human reading this said...

Amen.

PS: You can still use your order number (when you buy any version of the book from any retailer) to access the Rich as F*ck Book Party replay. Link in bio. (Truly, you want the money meditation inside. And my riffs on debt, wealth, releasing the ‘how’, ect.)

Have you bought a copy? Let me know below!!

.
I am so excited to bring you this free Morning Meditation for Manifesting designed to support you in transforming your day.

Now, of course, we know that transformation + growth are both ways of life and life long journeys.

We also know, however, that moments of feeling better, moments of intentionally creating, moments of dreaming, moments of letting it be ease, moments of envisioning and imagining, moments of action and strategic + smart effort... all add up. The moments add up.

And next thing we know, we have a whole new life.

As this year ends, it's time to begin again. It's time to step into your life's flow. It's time to choose who we will be and where we will go. It's time to trust ourselves more.

This is a meditation for guidance, protection, love and abundance.

Remember: You are deeply taken care of. You are fully protected. You are incredibly loved.

Feel into that truth. Feel into that universal truth. Feel that in your body.

From this place of love -- everything comes.

Say it with me: I love myself fully. I trust myself completely. I am willing to let it be easier. I am ready to see things differently. I am here for growth, love, belonging, acceptance, love, abundance, and so much pure joy. I get to where I desire to go with grace and ease. My desires arrive naturally. I am always being guided.

I am excited to see you create and design your best life -- while allowing this morning meditation for manifesting to support you in transforming your day in less than ten minutes.

We keep this short at 8:08 so you can come back to this whenever you need it! I love you!

node.title: Let it Be Easy — Morning Meditation

.
I'm sure there is a place for patience (in the manifestation process) -- I just haven't found it yet.

^^ things I say while teaching lol

For today's video, the team AF and I have pulled a couple riffs from a recent hour+ long training I taught.

In the video I share answers to some of your most popular Qs.

I share on...

>> How to move out of a waiting energy and into a watching energy when it comes to creating your desires (no patience required!)

>> Defining + deciding how people think of you, relate to you, and know you online and in life (we often call this "branding")

(This has something to do with how certain people seem to pull off + get away with stuff we feel we couldn't. Watch for more.)

>> Journal prompts + inner work vibes to support you in creating an intentional and solid brand + presence

For a third Q+A moment, hop over to my podcast, where we share a longer version of this video and include a riff on...

>> Integrating social media sharing into your full life + daily experience so don't feel like you have so f*ing much to do (Episode 111)

Remember, loves: Our manifestations take a period of time on the human plane (in the physical realm). It may seems slow, but it helps to remember that you can have it because you can. Because you are moving toward it, because you are aligning with it, because you are a match for it, because you are calling it in, because you are acting + living + being + believing as though it is yours. Because you've decided.

Your world -- as you know it -- is rearranging for you to have what you've chosen. You energetic decision and declarations are that powerful.

It's not really about patience or being okay with the slowness. Yes, notice when something is not here yet and process the fear or frustration that brings up.

Then watch for the evidence that it's coming. Add up the evidence. Add up the proof. See the signs and indications of what is coming through.

You wait for nothing. You watch for what is soon to be yours. You choose your focus. You allow your feelings to follow.

You move into the confidence + certainty + knowing of what you've chosen.

Got it? I love you.

What do you think? Let me know bel

node.text:
▫️Elevate yourself.

Let the noise fade away.

Ascend. Climb. Fly. Soar.

Rise up into all you were made for.

▫️Isolate yourself.

Blinders on. Tunnel vision. Focused on what matters.

Decided. Unbothered. Sure.

Noticing as the nonsense dissolves into nothingness.

▫️Solidify yourself.

Build your own foundation.

Place yourself on secure ground.

Standing with God. Unstoppable. Unshakable.

▫️Hold yourself.

Generate your own calm, confidence and certainty.

Observe from above the chaos.

Creating your shelter in the storm.

▫️Love (the f* out of) yourself.

Seeing, embracing, and relishing in all that you are.

Delighting in the magnificence that is you.

Liking who you are.

▫️Separate yourself.

Identify distractions. Notice who spins out over silliness.

Knowing who and what isn’t right for you.

Choosing who gets to be in your world.

▫️Secure yourself.

Incubate your dreams. Guard your heart.

Be clear on what gets past the barrier of your inner peace.

Know where walls are needed.

▫️Nurture yourself.

Recognize who (and what) is good for your heart. Let them in.

Let them love you. Let them help you.

Form a cocoon of nourishing love and peace with your chosen humans.

Relish in the love.

▫️Give of yourself.

Give with your words, your love, your heart.

Give generously. Give intentionally.

Give from love and never guilt or obligation.

Ask for nothing in return.

▫️Choose yourself.

You are the leader of your life and world.

Pick up your crown. Take your place.

Who better to have a good life than you?

▫️I’ll say it again: Elevate yourself.

You’re responsible for you. Let’s make the most of it.

Intentional. Purposeful. Determined.

Always on the move.

Always on the rise.

Elevating. Always.

Pictured: A moment in New York. 🖤

node.text:
Respect.

People try to force it. Demand it. Obligate others toward giving it.

"I am the boss." "I am your mother." “Know your place."

They try to create it with threats, anger, or obligation -- creating blind obedience at worst and defiance at best.

Example One: Work. Year’s ago, I started my business and needed support. I was on edge with my team -- my biggest fearing being that my company might not work. I was hard on people. Every mistake felt like a crisis. I was often consumed by someone's perceived f* up. My lack of emotional regulation and grounded-ness ripped through the company. No one could thrive.

Alternative: Today, I trust my team. I want their opinions and insights. I convey my needs and desires. I give them space and choices. I let them do their jobs. Nothing is a crisis. (There was truly never any crisis.) We have a calm and thriving work culture.

Remember: You are the boss. That is not in question.

Example Two: Children. Care-givers sometimes use intimidation tactics. "You WILL do what I say." The child may scream, run away, or cower down (fight, flight, freeze). Once the child is broken down and does what they were told, it seems like the adult “won”. In actuality, we f*ed with their nervous system. They felt like our love and their safety were in jeopardy so, they obeyed.

Alternative: Trust kids. See them. Connect with them. Work with their need for independence. Provide consistent boundaries. Prep them for situations. Give them space and choices.

Remember: You are the adult. That's not in question.

Force creates fear. People can not learn or thrive in fear. (Neurologically impossible.)

Respect comes from BEING a the leader, not the person who must remind you they are one.

As always, the things we want are created from how we be -- not what we say, do or demand.

We can conduct ourselves in such a way where those around us feel safe with us, want us to be happy, desire to do well and, naturally... have respect for us.

No force, threat or demand required.

Let’s lead from love. Conduct ourselves with calm. Trust ourselves.

And each other.

There is no need to demand anything when you can create everything. ♥️

What do you think?

node.text:
Remember: Money is not limited. And neither are we.

When you have never viewed yourself as a “rich” person or felt that wealth was a real possibility for you, you may accidently judge everyone whom you imagine that reality came easily to. 

I know what this is like. I have struggled with judgement toward people whom I believed had financial success that was obtained easily or handed to them. I’ve judged people who did not need to work— “rich kids” and "trust-fund babies." 

These are not pretty parts of me.

It’s easy to take on an us-vs-them mentality when you mistakenly believe that someone is innately different from you at your core. All of us have love, truth, and God at our core. (Our dysfunctional ways of being are not the ultimate truth of who we are—they are coping mechanisms we established to feel safe in an unpredictable world.)

Looking down upon people for having what you want, is a very effective way to judge yourself out of getting what you want.

Judging people for having money is a very effective way to repel money. If you think rich people are greedy, bad, selfish, or wrong, you won’t allow yourself to become rich.

In my financial life, I have found that one of the most helpful things I can do is release the duality around the thing I want.

When we want what we want, allow ourselves to want it, embrace that we want it, accept that we want it, and determine to do good with it as we receive it . . . our energy is potent.

We are confident and sure. >> Our intentional and unintentional attractions are magnified. << We are clean and clear inside of ourselves.

- an excerpt from my book, Rich as F*ck

Grab the book today for some serious codes, insights and receptivity around money. 

(Including a story I didn’t have room for above — when I got myself sabotaging myself by judging a “rich lady” in first class.)

Pictured: Unicorn Princess Party Prep with the angel baby girl. 🦄

node.text:
The Wealthy Woman loves herself.

Abundance is her state of mind.

Abundance is her way of life.

She can't escape it, because she is it.

She lives and embodies the wealth that is her.

She listens to her soul. She answers the call.

She allows her courage and heart to lead the way.

She knows her greatness. She embraces her gifts. 
She dances through darkness. She creates miracles with her presence.

She stands in her truth, her worth, and her love.

She is real. She is true. She is confident. She is sure.

She is the breading grounds and holding place for her own wealth.

She is The Wealthy Woman.

Embodiment is not just what you do; It’s how you be.

How you be: What you do naturally, without trying + with repeatable results. It is what you create with your presence + energy + decisions.

When you work on who and how we be... you are able to embody, get comfortable with, feel safe with, allow in without forcing, and begin to maintain new levels of abundance.

You have become The Wealthy Woman. (This is much more sustainable than traditional manifesting.)

>> I consider it my duty to expand financially. <<

It is my job to prepare and position myself for increase -- in my spending, saving, donating, investing, receiving, generating, etc.

(This is what The Wealthy Woman does.)

>> Then it is my job to tell you everything I've learned, grown into and come to understand. <<

And, even more so, it is my job to speak to you from the place that created my results.

The Wealthy Woman Bundle was recorded in 2020 and 2021.

There is an energy of confidence, certainty, and progress -- and, because I am me, the topic of money is made simple, clear, concise and easy to understand.

It is your job to prepare and position ourselves for all you want.

We have to condition the soil. We have to clear out the weeds. We have to make some intentional choices about who you are, how you be and what you choose with money.

We have to decide to become The Wealthy Woman before it seems possible to do so.

This is final call for the special price on my newest video training bundle. LINK IN BIO. I wouldn't wait.

Are you in? Would love to hear from you! ♥️♥️♥️ Qs? Ask below!

node.text:
The Wealthy Woman trusts herself.

She knows who she is. She knows what she stands for.

She trusts herself with money — to generate it, receives it, release it and use it well.

She knows she can always generate more.

The Wealthy Woman does not play small or blame others.

She shows up, does her thing and takes responsibility for her life.

The Wealthy Woman elevates herself.

And yet is working with something greater — an energy of love and power — that is always by her side.

Solid. Strong. Confident. Sure. Flowing. Trusting.

She is force. An empire in and of herself.

Say it with me: I am the wealthy woman. ♥️

node.text:
Why do women like to learn from me about money?

I make money easy. I make money feel good.

I have a really good relationship with money and I didn't always.

Growing up, the subject of money was drenched in fear, restriction, and panic.

I felt held back by money. Limited. And like the realities around my finances were always in my way.

I have, clearly, transformed the sh*t out of this.

The thing I want you to understand is this: Getting money isn't what changes things.

Getting money isn't what makes you feel worthy of money, safe with money, and good with money.

Getting money doesn't resolve your issues with money. Resolving your issues with money, resolves your issues with money. And, as a result, often gets you more money.

The internal has to change.

The beliefs, mindset and inner experience has to change.

>> Hear me: You are the breeding grounds and the holding place for the money in your life. <<

We must prepare and condition the soil, clear out the weeds, and make some intentional choices about who you are, how you be and what you choose with money.

Position yourself. Make room. Decide who you will be. Prepare for your expansion.

I made the decision inside of myself, way before it was created in my physical world, to be The Wealthy Woman.

The principles, concepts and ways of thinking that I share can be applied to, well, anything.

They not limited to a certain industry or career or lifestyle. They are for everyone.

Embodying the Wealthy Woman is a way of seeing yourself, a way of positioning yourself, and a way of thinking of, well, everything.

It's about your identity. It's about what you know to be true... about you.

With that in mind, it is a joy to invite you to The Wealthy Woman.

This is my newest video training bundle -- recorded in 2020 and 2021.

You have all content + unlimited replays + any future updates for life when you enroll.

If you missed the introductory price last week, do not worry.

There is a special price for you happening... now.

Client feedback + payment options + details: LINK IN BIO

The sale ends Friday. I wouldn't wait. I love you!

Are you in? Let me know! Already enrolled? Would love to hear from you!

node.text:
Sometimes, it’s the simple things. 🖤

Realizing you have absolutely nothing on your schedule… for the first time since you can remember.

Fresh flowers from the neighbor shop.

A box of chocolates and a new candle.

Clean hair. A flowy dress. A self timer moment.

A quiet house. A long walk. A warm bath.

Your favorite latte. A happy Friday.

A day with no makeup.

Working on a project your jazzed about.

Knowing you’re where you want to me.

Trusting yourself with your next steps.

Knowing your doing a good job.

Being happy with what you’ve created.

Giving yourself a little credit.

Enjoying what you’ve worked hard on.

Having best time alone… with yourself.

Being happy with who you are.

Walking to meet your loves for dinner at the end of the day.

Sometimes, it’s the simple things.

Pic: My afternoon in my little black and white kitchen.

🖤🦓🐼🐈‍⬛🤍

node.text:
The Wealthy Woman. (One Day Sale!)

She trusts herself.

She is confident and sure.

She knows who she is. And she knows what she stands for.

She trusts herself with money -- to generate it and receive it; to spend, save, invest and donate... to use it well.

She knows better than to obsess over what could go wrong.

She knows the energy of money is limitless.

She knows she can always generate more.

She knows it is safe to relax, live, rest, trust, flow and... be.

She knows her mission. She's in here lane. She's here on purpose.

She focused, yet flowing. She strong, yet sensitive.

She's human. She's real. And she knows her mother f*ing power.

The Wealthy Woman does not shrink down, play small, or blame others.

She shows up and designs her life.

The Wealthy Woman builds herself up.

And yet, it is clear, she is working with something greater -- an energy of love and power -- that she knows is always by her side.

She is a force. An empire in and of herself.

She is you. She is me.

She is us when we are in our power, full of trust, strength, intention and love.

It is time to remember who tf you are and to embody the most radiant and wealthy you.

It is a joy and an honor to invite you to my newest digital training bundle: The Wealthy Woman.

It's about money, but it's also about you.

It's about who you are, how you show up in this world and what that creates. It's about standing in your worth and claiming your power. It about stepping into your next iteration of growth and abundance while creating an empowered financial reality.

It's about becoming The Wealthy Woman -- the queen of money in your life and world.

All videos were recorded in 2020 and 2021. (The first three videos were recorded as AFI was generating $450k a month. The final video was recorded as AFI generated a $750k in a month for the first time.)

As always, you have all content + any future updates when you enroll in this program.

Feedback + payment options + details: Link in bio

^^ ONE DAY SALE. SPECIAL INTRODUCTORY PRICE!

The introductory price is available for today only. I wouldn't wait.

(After that the price will go up 33% for a few days before the final price takes effect.)

node.text:
>> Releasing high conflict, chaotic, energetically messy people <<

You know that feeling when someone’s nonsense is getting too close to you?

Like their hurricane, train wreck, bulldozer or vampire like ways of conducting themselves is… in your space.

Or the stuff in their head has been projected on to you and instead of observing, releasing and living your life… you’re impacted.

You feel slimmed or caught in their sticky web after coming in contact or even thinking about them.

It’s time to detangle yourself. You do not belong in the messy web that is their way of living.

Listen: It’s up to us what we engage with, what we give weight and power to, and what we let take up space inside of us.

We have to observe the crazy without becoming one with the crazy.

We have to let their stuff mean nothing about us.

We also have to look at why they get to us. (Good Q: What are re afraid these interactions mean about us and our future?)

Say it with me: I am not required to engage with the doubt filled, small minded or fear based thinking of those I come in contact with. I am creating my life. They are creating theirs. My results and my reality speak for itself.

Detach. Close the door. Seal it. Imagine their energy and impact dissolving, releasing and leaving your space.

Perhaps you’ll need to say something to set new standards, norm or boundary with this person. 

Or maybe you won’t... as your energy, detachment, standards and certainty will do the talking for you.

Either way: Let them go. Decline the energetic invitation to engage. Release. Move on. Send them love…

And live your f*ing life.

Be free. I love you. ♥️

node.text:
My mom sent me a link of a the car she would get if she “won the lottery” last week.

So, I bought one just like it.

I love you, Mom and Dad.

I appreciate you more than I can explain.

I know I wasn’t the easiest child to raise, but you let me be me, make my choices, and live my life… fully.

It might be a weird thing to say, but thank you for never getting in my way as I formed my dreams, life and path.

Turns out… that’s exactly what I needed.

Enjoy your MERCEDES! ♥️♥️♥️

Special thanks to Jason at @mb_batonrouge for all your help!!

And to @kimhamiltonn_ for, per usual, facilitating one of my crazy ideas.
